A vintage-style illustration of a phoenix rising from scattered computer circuit boards and old floppy disks, rendered in warm sepia and amber tones reminiscent of 1970s poster art. The majestic bird emerges with spread wings against a backdrop featuring the iconic silhouette of Singapore's Marina Bay skyline at dusk. Delicate wisps of smoke and ember particles swirl around the phoenix, transforming into abstract mobile device shapes as they drift upward. The composition uses bold, confident linework with halftone dot patterns typical of vintage printing techniques. Rich burgundy, gold, and deep teal accent colors pop against the aged paper texture background, conveying themes of community revival, technological rebirth, and the enduring spirit of passionate tech enthusiasts gathering together again.
